config MTK_OTP
	bool "MTK One-Time-Programmable Support"
	default n
	help
	  MTK One-Time-Programmable (i.e. OTP or EFUSE Run-Time Blowing)
	  APIs provide the mechanism for blowing, reading or to re-init
	  specific EFUSE customer fields in kernel or MD side. It helps
	  to set the PMIC to the correct settings for OTP and maintains
	  a mutex for solving currency issue.
